data.title: Andy & Evan
data.meta_description:
Andy & Evan | 469 followers on LinkedIn. Andy & Evan is a clothing brand for children sold at better retailers worldwide. The Andy & Evan name has become synonymous with updated-traditional fashion, an abundance of detail, and great quality. 

Our mission is to simplify the lives of parents, and make kids happy.
